place.name: KINLOCHBERVIE
place.gazetteerText: Kinlochbervie, quoad sacra par. and hamlet, Eddrachillis par., NW. Sutherlandshire--par., pop. 920; hamlet, on N. side of Loch Inchard, 3½ miles NW. of Rhiconich; P.O. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
